OL,3,CBoss of P&O Ferries admits paying crew
OL,4,Cas little as #4.87 per hour
OL,6,FPeter Hebblethwaite told MPs on the
OL,7,FBusiness and Trade Committee that the
OL,8,Fdecision to fire 786 staff in March
OL,9,F2022 and replace them with low paid
OL,10,Fagency crew was "difficult" and "one
OL,11,Fwhich I wish we'd never had to make in
OL,12,Fthe first place".
OL,14,FBut he insisted it was a decision that
OL,15,Fhad saved the company from bankruptcy.
OL,17,FAt the time of the mass sackings two
OL,18,Fyears ago, Mr Hebblethwaite told
OL,19,Fparliamentarians that the lowest paid
OL,20,Fagency worker was earning at least
OL,21,F#5.15 an hour.
