OL,3,CBoss of P&O Ferries admits paying crew
OL,4,Cas little as #4.87 per hour
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, he admitted the some crew
OL,7,Fare currently being paid as little as
OL,8,F#4.87 an hour, including holiday pay,
OL,9,Fovertime and bonuses.
OL,11,FTwo months ago, when ITV News and the
OL,12,FGuardian reported that that we had
OL,13,Fseen payslips and contracts which
OL,14,Fshowed that some crew were earning
OL,15,Fprecisely this figure, P&O denied it.
