OL,3,CBoss of P&O Ferries admits paying crew
OL,4,Cas little as #4.87 per hour
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the company told us
OL,7,F"we do not recognise the pay rates
OL,8,Fthat you are referencing. No member of
OL,9,Four crew on our Dover-Calais vessels
OL,10,Fearns less than $5200 per month,
OL,11,Fequivalent to #5.20 per hour".
OL,13,F, also highlighted the long hours that
OL,14,Fsome of P&O's crew - many of whom are
OL,15,Frecruited from India, Malaysia and The
OL,16,FPhilippines - have been working.
OL,18,FWe spoke to more than a dozen
OL,19,Fseafarers on P&Os ships. They told us
OL,20,Fthey worked 84 hour weeks for up to
OL,21,Ffour months, without time ashore.
