OL,6,FMr Hebblethwaite appeared to dispute
OL,7,Fthis and told MPs that P&O contracted
OL,8,Fcrew via an agency on the basis they
OL,9,Fwould receive seven days off a month.
OL,11,FPeter Hebblethwaite, chief executive
OL,12,Fof P&O Ferries was questioned over the
OL,13,Ffindings of a joint investigation by
OL,14,FITV News and the Guardian
