OL,3,CBoss of P&O Ferries admits paying crew
OL,4,Cas little as #4.87 per hour
OL,6,FThe chairman of the committee, Liam
OL,7,FByrne, said: "Both ITV and the
OL,8,FGuardian found people working 12
OL,9,Fshifts, 7 days a week, for up to 17
OL,10,Fweeks at a time without a day off and
OL,11,Fwithout permission to leave the ship.
OL,12,FYou've just told the committee that
OL,13,Fpeople have seven days off a month"
OL,15,FMr Hebblethwaite replied: "The
OL,16,FMaritime Labour Convention requires
OL,17,Fseafarers to have a minimum of 2 and a
OL,18,Fhalf days off per month. On Dover-
OL,19,FCalais, we contract for seven days
OL,20,Foff.".
