OL,6,F"So the conclusions of this
OL,7,Finvestigation, from ITV and the
OL,8,FGuardian, are wrong?" Byrne asked.
OL,10,FMr Hebblethwaite paused and Mr Byrne
OL,11,Fpressed "is that a yes?"
OL,13,F"I can only tell you what we do," Mr
OL,14,FHebblethwaite responded.
OL,16,FFollowing the hearing, a number of P&O
OL,17,Fseafarers have contacted ITV News and
OL,18,Fthe Guardian to confirm that agency
OL,19,Fcrew do not receive days off.
